title: elf Studio High Definition Loose Face Powder
description: The e.l.f. High Definition Powder is a translucent, versatile loose powder that creates a flawless, "soft focus" effect to the skin. Masks fine lines and imperfections for a glowing, radiant complexion. This incredibly soft and invisible powder is ideal for everyday wear, either alone or over your favorite e.l.f. foundation. Our HD Powder is a makeup artist and e.l.f. customer favorite.

title: Coastal Scents Shadow Worx Matte Eye Primer, 0.676 Fluid Ounce
description: Have you been looking for something to help your eye shadow last longer throughout the day? If so, you've found the right primer. It offers multi-functional uses with ease. Your shadows will apply smoothly like silk, blend well and dry quickly. The slim tip point allows for precise dispersal of product. Whether your shadow is matte or shimmer, it will remain crease-free and vibrant all day.
